divs: Sighting DetailsI took this picture of a rainbow in Eastcote, London today. when I looked at the picture on a PC later I saw a metallic blob just below the rainbow. I didnt notice it when I took the photo. This blob was not on the photo that i took seconds later Not a clue what this blob is as I see plenty of planes in this area but never anything like this.
trends: There have been no other sightings in Eastcote
This sighting has never been favorited.
Summary: object captured on photo of rainbow
